id: pm-4i73
title: "Test meaningfulness audit: strengthen hollow assertions, de-mock thin specs, convert contract source-mirrors to behavior"
description: "Four-way audit of the 263-spec suite for hollow/tautological/over-mocked tests, followed by remediation on feat/extreme-quality-gates. Verified live: coverage 100/100/100/100 (32772/32772 stmts), 5312 tests green, jscpd 0 clones incl. tests, pragma budget 498/498 burn-down."
